      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PYRENEES ACE (8) trailed the lead and fought on well to be beaten 5.5 lengths into second (23.11) at this track in a Mix 3/4 over 410m. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Can go on with it. IT'S BUBBLE TIME (5) has a strong record this track and trip with five wins and two placings from nine starts. Was out of the placings last time (26.44) at Warragul in a Grade 5, finishing eighth and beaten 6 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. IS HE HAPPY (7) jumped well from a low draw and lead for much way to score when second (23.54) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 410m. Can feature again. STOJANOVIC (4) scored with plenty to spare last time. Big chance on that form.",
